</svg>
NTHC Prestige Homes, Nmai Zorm-Adjigarno Road
            </h2>
            <button type="submit" class="w-auto text-white bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-gray-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5 text-center dark:bg-gray-600 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:focus:ring-gray-800">Get directions</button>


        </div>
        <div class=" p-4  bgColor rounded-lg md:p-8 " id="statistics" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="statistics-tab">
